/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n淺草雷門同明治神宮必去啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n另外台場我覺得都幾好行幾舒服（唔怕近海好凍既話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ) 坐海鷗線睇下景都幾正</blockquote><br />\n淺草雷門就唔好啦  人多到咩咁  <br />\n上野恩賜公園幾好行   又無咩人  好運既可能有幾棵櫻花開左  你會唔會去近郊   去的話比較推薦伊東個頭   因為好寧靜   不過最好住一兩晚"},{"pid":"f16b8bbf6d59199c708cefed749ad326969f80eb","tid":134050,"uid":49868,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-25T09:48:50.000Z","msg":"帶屋企人自駕算喇，坐鐵路應該會屌哂老味"},{"pid":"0bc152f0a53838ad2104f3b7fae8f0603d3c7df1","tid":134050,"uid":40171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-25T10:03:05.000Z","msg":"去邊度好睇兩老嘅年紀、喜好同埋體力<br />\n40/50 同 60/70 鍾意嘅嘢好唔同，啱去嘅地方都會唔同<br />\n<br />\n帶長輩自由行，年紀大嘅會對住宿同埋交通比較有要求，要以舒服、方便為優先<br />\n年紀輕啲嘅可能會對食、購物比較有要求<br />\n講到尾知道佢哋鍾意乜嘢好重要<br />\n<br />\n利申：帶過兩老日本鐵路自由行，so-far都冇乜事"},{"pid":"5ad68c37def231dfae68a3e4eb7c6fbf97fda2f8","tid":134050,"uid":67377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-26T16:34:17.000Z","msg":"好睇兩老咩年紀 帶過雙親(50頭)8日東京<br />\n都冇乜野 做好曬research 食野每個地方search定有咩好食<br />\n都應該冇乜事嘅"},{"pid":"5241bcb5d777235ca355cecb2ab91ef6a2bdc1c7","tid":134050,"uid":30565,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-26T17:56:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好睇兩老咩年紀 帶過雙親(50頭)8日東京<br />\n都冇乜野 做好曬research 食野每個地方search定有咩好食<br />\n都應該冇乜事嘅</blockquote><br />\n50頭 不過帶佢地去明治神宮睇下都唔錯<br />\n皇居果d <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c866c9ec3fee95a4f626d2babf8dde245e88bf37","tid":134050,"uid":86901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-26T20:48:47.000Z","msg":"淺草吾妻橋嗰度有19遊覽船坐去台場<br />\n應該會好啱兩老<br />\n<br />\n仲有個地方叫三崎口<br />\n絲打可以search下<br />\n有one day pass包晒來回車費 嗰度巴士 同餐lunch<br />\n<br />\n利申 帶過兩老去大阪東京名古屋 最癲去過瑞士"},{"pid":"a9098f4033f6bc499766ea9da130bbebc3dac8c1","tid":134050,"uid":71473,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-26T23:28:09.000Z","msg":"同兩老出去，旅行團就發揮作用了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"426a2a1b64aef0231ea566d56d15e24da15bbb61","tid":134050,"uid":3937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-27T05:48:01.000Z","msg":"睇你兩老合唔合作<br />\n<br />\n同夫人兩老去過日本歐洲自由行<br />\n兩老都好合作<br />\n所以好順利<br />\n<br />\n之前去東京都係櫻花季節<br />\n去左<br />\n新宿御苑<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.env.go.jp/garden/shinjukugyoen/2_guide/access.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.env.go.jp%2Fgarden%2Fshinjukugyoen%2F2_guide%2Faccess.html&d=PG0fnU9ECAVDedUX85NM%2FG6kGZraZVKwHE52VSkiKoI%3D&h=5839d165\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.env.go.jp/garden/shinjukugyoen/2_guide/access.html</a><br />\n上野恩賜公園<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.kensetsu.metro.tokyo.jp/toubuk/ueno/map.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.kensetsu.metro.tokyo.jp%2Ftoubuk%2Fueno%2Fmap.html&d=PG0fnU9ECAVDedUX85NM%2FG6kGZraZVKwHE52VSkiKoI%3D&h=e25a7c4f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.kensetsu.metro.tokyo.jp/toubuk/ueno/map.html</a><br />\n千鳥ケ淵<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.env.go.jp/garden/kokyogaien/2_guide/access.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.env.go.jp%2Fgarden%2Fkokyogaien%2F2_guide%2Faccess.html&d=PG0fnU9ECAVDedUX85NM%2FG6kGZraZVKwHE52VSkiKoI%3D&h=26e8d94a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.env.go.jp/garden/kokyogaien/2_guide/access.html</a><br />\n伊豆高原<br />\n輕井澤<br />\n<br />\n而家好似有得睇河津櫻<br />\n你可以睇下"}]}